  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="transcription" xml:id="transcription_aad_0054" xml:lang="de">
        <div type="envelope">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00219/" ed="1r" type="envelope"/>
          <ab hand="#type_black_auden" xml:lang="en">
            <lb/><space quantity="21" unit="char"/><hi rend="underline" hand="#type_black_auden">Air-Mail</hi>
          </ab>
          <ab hand="#type_black_auden" xml:lang="en">
            <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">W.H.Auden</rs>
            <address>
              <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_29">77 St Mark's Place
              <lb/>New York City
              <lb/>New York IOOO3
              <lb/>U.S.A.</rs>
            </address>
          </ab>
          <ab hand="#type_black_auden">
            <lb/><space quantity="24" unit="char"/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_107">Herrn Hugo Kurka</rs>
            <address>
              <lb/><space quantity="26" unit="char"/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_356">Wien XX
              <lb/><space quantity="27" unit="char"/>Adalbert Stiftergasse 22/28
              <lb/><space quantity="28" unit="char"/><foreign xml:lang="en">Austria</foreign></rs>
            </address>   
          </ab>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00220/" ed="1v" type="envelope"/>
        </div>
        <div type="letter">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00221/" ed="2r" type="sheet"/>
          <div type="letter_message" hand="#type_black_auden">
            <opener>
              <dateline>
                <placeName>
                  <address xml:lang="en">
                    <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_29">77 St Mark's Place
                    <lb/>New York City
                    <lb/>New York IOOO3</rs>
                  </address>
                </placeName>
                <date>
                  <lb/><space quantity="34" unit="char"/>IIten,Januar
                </date>
              </dateline>
              <salute>
                <lb/><space quantity="26" unit="char"/><del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">Liber</del> Lieber <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_107">Hugo</rs>:
              </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
              <lb/><space quantity="19" unit="char"/>Besten Dank fur deinen zwei Briefe. Endlich habe ich von
              <lb/><space quantity="15" unit="char"/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_14">Redlich</rs> geh<g ref="#uml_o_lc_tt">ö</g>rt. Er sagte,zum beispeil<unclear>:</unclear>
              <seg>
                <lb/><space quantity="11" unit="char"/>"Der schult<subst><del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">a</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#type_black_auden">r</add></subst>agende Lenker <del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">was</del> wurde bereits verhaftet und sitzt beim
                <lb/><space quantity="12" unit="char"/><rs type="org" ref="#amp_organization_100">Kreisgericht St.P<g ref="#uml_o_lc_tt">ö</g>lten</rs>. Er war betrunken und h<g ref="#uml_a_lc_tt">ä</g><subst><del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">r</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#type_black_auden">t</add></subst>te auch keinen
                <lb/><space quantity="12" unit="char"/>F<g ref="#uml_u_lc_tt">ü</g>hrerschein.Wie mir die <rs type="org" ref="#amp_organization_101">Gendar<subst><del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">,</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#type_black_auden">m</add></subst>erie</rs> mitteilte,hat er 20 Vorstrafen.
                <lb/><space quantity="12" unit="char"/>Die letze in der Dauer von einem Jahr hat er noch nicht abge<add place="above" hand="#hand_blue_auden">ge</add>ssen.<add place="inline" hand="#hand_blue_auden">"</add>
              </seg>
              <seg>
                <lb/><space quantity="11" unit="char"/>"Das Auto liegt in <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_47">Neulengbach</rs>,total besch<g ref="#uml_a_lc_tt">ä</g>digt."
              </seg>
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/><space quantity="11" unit="char"/>Die <del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">einziste</del> einzigste gute Na<unclear><subst><del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden"><subst><del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">h</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#type_black_auden">c</add></subst></del><add place="superimposed" hand="#type_black_auden">c</add></subst></unclear>htricht:
              <seg>
                <lb/><space quantity="11" unit="char"/>" Der Wagen des s<add place="above" hand="#hand_blue_auden">c</add>huldtrage<subst><del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">gen</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#type_black_auden">nde</add></subst>n Lenkers war versichert,so dass die
                <lb/><space quantity="13" unit="char"/>Versicherungs-Gesellschaft <space quantity="1" unit="char"/>f<g ref="#uml_u_lc_tt">ü</g>r den Schaden aufzukommen haben wird."
              </seg>
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/><space quantity="13" unit="char"/>Die Schaden werden hoch sein,weil mit<rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_23">Iannis</rs> waren <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_258" ana="#ana_078">zwei Amerikarin</rs>: ein
              <lb/><space quantity="13" unit="char"/>war schwer verlezt,<del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">der</del> die anderer leicht.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/><space quantity="13" unit="char"/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_14">Redlich</rs> ist pensionie<subst><del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">t</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#type_black_auden">r</add></subst>t,so dass f<g ref="#uml_u_lc_tt">ü</g>r den Prozess ich habe einen
              <lb/><space quantity="13" unit="char"/>neuen Advokat,ein <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_235">Dr Mikesch</rs>.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/><space quantity="13" unit="char"/>Ich schriebe mein Ver<subst><del rend="overtyped" hand="#type_black_auden">i</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#type_black_auden">s</add></subst>icherungsgesellschaft so fort.
            </p>
            <closer>
              <salute>
                <lb/><space quantity="28" unit="char"/>immer dein Freund
              </salute>
              <signed hand="#hand_blue_auden">
                <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">Wystan</rs>
              </signed>
            </closer>
          </div>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00222/" ed="2v" type="sheet"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
